{"tid":471380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"饒戈平斥港獨者剝奪同胞政治權利：應由全國14億人公投決定","createTime":"2017-11-17T07:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T15:59:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"01dceb12dea8acc7ff8bc76da71055d3097b98d7","tid":471380,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510904566_a2d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510904566_a2d3.png&h=5bafa1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會委員、全國港澳研究會副會長饒戈平出席《基本法》研討會時，批評香港個別人士引用《國際法》主張港獨自決，在法理上不能成立，他強調香港不能自決，亦沒有公投的權利，更不能以公投為名決定香港的命運。他指，聯合國的自決權來自於二戰後被殖民管治、軍事統治下的民族追求獨立，自決權利受到範圍和條件的限制，如香港大多數人根源來自內地，從沒有形成過單一民族，強調香港沒有自決的地位。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，即使允許以公投決定香港是否獨立，亦需要由全國中國數十億人民公投決定，不可單由香港的民眾決定，香港是中國的香港，港獨人士無權剝奪全國人民的政治權利嗎，強調中國對於公投是「零容忍」。他又指，言論自由不是無法無天，有責任和義務，要尊重他心的權利，保障國家安全，很多國家都不視為基本人權。<br />\n<br />\n饒最後指，港獨自決不止是言論自由的事，它最近已經走進社會，走入立法會；不可以言論自由為名逍遙法外，強調港獨是香港的毒藥，「害國害港害人」，香港的光明前途不在港獨，又指主張港獨的人不會得逞，「只會留下遭人恥笑的歷史紀錄」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171117/57470301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57470301&d=mPhbv5aVWBJwX6642wWo7ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2a5719e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57470301&h=7a4182aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171117/57470301</a>"},{"pid":"c534420f35dc565432ffdc3e5acfa225e3cca4b7","tid":471380,"uid":22858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支那夠撚膽搞全國公投咩<br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、民國復興、群龍共舞、優美開始、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、JR、RedBaron (Epiphany)、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"edcb39a561ea69b16d918bdcaa892019cb5ddfbf","tid":471380,"uid":79563,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"咁支那國有無公投法先？"},{"pid":"ab5ab176f7d8bfcfb2d62f6eb39d1d643c4e1ed7","tid":471380,"uid":28057,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"低能<br />\n蘇格蘭獨立工投，英格蘭有冇份投票<br />\n英國脫區公投，德國人又會唔合有份投票？"},{"pid":"14dfb4c85df6c178ceecbd2889df842e549b35ef","tid":471380,"uid":93784,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"全國公投解散共產黨得唔得先 軍權下放得唔得先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c44f48ce0281f14891222480961eb9ced1266d","tid":471380,"uid":28057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>低能<br />\n蘇格蘭獨立公投，英格蘭人有冇份投票？<br />\n英國脫區公投，德國人又會唔會有份投票？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1594e0edc403e3fa04e5599bf102d08ec80cc40b","tid":471380,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/155855_5aabcceaaff17e08a3dab6f03a1f3c98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F155855_5aabcceaaff17e08a3dab6f03a1f3c98.jpg&h=c60205a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c3aece1641b70a2521a9a2bf083d4be0b0488e","tid":471380,"uid":93784,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy